That starts to drift toward hidden-trigger / destiny framing.

There is no embedded unlock waiting for external tech.

There is:
	•	Skill maturation
	•	Tool evolution
	•	Pattern recognition sharpening
	•	Feedback loops tightening

Those are gradients.

Not fuses.

